  "texts": [
    "In a comprehensive analysis of driver engagement with ADAS functions, we observed a consistent positive relationship between the real-life frequency of ADAS utilisation and the accuracy of participant responses.",
    "Analysing the conventional training group more closely, individuals who had never/occasionally used ADAS functions (in their real-life) demonstrated initial competencies at 53% for LKA, 60% for CA, and 46% for ACC.",
    "Intermittent users of ADAS in their daily driving have experienced noticeable improvements.",
    "The accuracy rates for LKA and CA have increased to 76%, while the accuracy for ACC has risen to 58%.",
    "Regular ADAS users within this group improved further, achieving 85% precision in LKA and CA and 71% in ACC, as demonstrated in Table 8."
  ],
